Alexa, check the house ---- turn on input_boolean.house_check
Alexa, turn on guest mode ---- turn on input_boolean.guest_mode
Alexa, The kids are staying home ---- turn on Guest Mode
Alexa, We are leaving ---- turn on input_boolean.fam_leaving
Alexa (your secret passphrase i.e. Alexa, the eagle has landed) ---- turn on input_boolean.(yoursecretboolean)
Alexa, the sky is falling ---- turn on input_boolean.panic
